This paper discusses the quantization of Cellular Neural Networks (CeNNs) for Cyber Physical Systems (CPSs), which involves topics related to embedded systems, computer vision, machine learning, control systems, and neural networks. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.ET (Embedded Systems), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
